1.1.name: wordpress/brunelleschi
1.1.description: Brunelleschi is a modern theme with emphasis on readability and clean typography. Brunelleschi includes a fully flexible mobile layout and a full HTML5 implementation, that way it looks great on any screen and on any modern browser. Brunelleschi also has lots of customizable options including page-width, multiple sidebars, featured content slider and more! Available in Belarusian, Czech, Dutch, English, French, German, Italian, Polish, Russian and Spanish.
